Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.01,0:01:01.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是却
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:06.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}总有一天愿望会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:10.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是「总有一天」是哪一天
