Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  光是得到了瓶子并不能代表什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用这个瓶子收集什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  要收集很多人受伤的心  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么收集？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须治愈受伤的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  看样子你基本上明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么马上就去收集吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  差点忘说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边有人在的时候不要和我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙没有知识记忆和常识  所以我告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的布娃娃是不能说话的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和不能说话的东西说话是很奇怪的  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是布娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么布娃娃就不能说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话  快干活去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  小鸠会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然从跷跷板上下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有受伤的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想被治愈的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我治愈你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…有人需要我治愈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有需要我帮忙的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪子布…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来当踢罐子的鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要当鬼就可以帮上忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢飞罐子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？好奇怪啊 里面还是什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当踢罐子的鬼算是哪门子的治愈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常来讲也没有这样就能治愈的受伤的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才做的只不过是陪人玩游戏而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要遇上想被治愈的人还真难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是…没有想被治愈的人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说明没有受伤或是悲伤的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙的神经到底要乐观到什么程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是可以找到帮忙的方法就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（今日开业  PANPAN  玛爷爷亲手做的牛肉饼）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请收下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…给我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  请您收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够毫不犹豫地将这样漂亮的东西和他人分享
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是多么高尚的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这么多需要发出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要是能多拿些就太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  那全都给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  帮了我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但帮了别人的忙  还得到了这么许多漂亮的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意你拿了一堆打算做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:06:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到我将这些漂亮的东西分发给大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下这些漂亮的纸巾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以帮上您的忙的 请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多给您一些…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请来拿吧  不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这漂亮的纸巾  请大家来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在路中间晃悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…是之前遇到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把纸巾收好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我向你道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得他是往这边走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床单飞走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师  这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子蹭破了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢死人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不可以笑话姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我是这所艾草托儿所的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为人手不足  所以没来得及收洗好的衣物…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手不足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您很为难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:07:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手不足的话  我可以帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以帮忙吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些  请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫俊彦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠？奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你爸爸叫大鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫什么名字呢  叫什么名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么…叫什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不要太调皮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…有什么需要我帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这样陪大家玩就已经帮我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪大家玩吗…唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹风琴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我不会弹风琴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是可以一起跳舞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  清和老师  来弹风琴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小鸠老师一起跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙不是老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟在我后面来这里有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？我只是想来道谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了  请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  人家已经让我在这里帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会弹风琴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你们是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是和我一起工作的藤本清和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是小鸠  今天一天就拜托你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别碍事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和老师  快点弹风琴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  快点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你们俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跳的那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个人真坏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我是不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠好好玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是孩子们住的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是住  只是白天孩子们被寄托在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  这里很旧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近也建起了新的幼儿园  来的孩子也渐渐变少了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能不加油了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  只是担心的话也没用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  就像藤本说的那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  帮我大忙了  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们也很开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有啦  我只是陪他们一起玩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是被猪尾吕义先生骂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  猪尾吕义先生不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有和你一起来的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  说是一起来的人  其实是一只布娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它不能说话  所以不去找它的话一定会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  明天我也可以来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以拜托你的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这样住在哪里在干什么都不清楚的家伙随便出入园里没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是不清楚呢  我是花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只说名字就算是回答了么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要小鸠方便的话我们很欢迎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是拿不出多少打工费来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只要能让我来帮忙就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提醒你一句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是因为同情或者好奇心的话就别来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻烦啊  被别人觉得可怜或是辛苦什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是突然被丢在路中间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能找到你太好了  猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好你个头！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲着别人的视线一点一点移动的辛苦你能明白吗  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了吧  在这里我是布娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布娃娃是不会自己走动的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是瓶子  连我都给忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓶子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么果然啊  你还以为会装进什么东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…我在做的事情不是在治愈他人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是… 在添麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生好像受过什么伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是藤本先生却说我是个麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这也得根据个人情况来看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上有受伤的人和没受伤的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受伤的人之中又有想被治愈的人和不想被治愈的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些我以前都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想治愈他们的吧  那么就去治啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不可以那种事等实际治了再去考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俊彦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不在托儿所呢  现在要回家去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是还要等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢秋千吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也不是特别喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不在这里多呆一会的话妈妈也来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:18:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈真的很努力  明明离婚了非常辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会给我做好早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还很温柔  是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不说「不好」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俊彦  今天妈妈也还没来接你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  俊彦真是个乖孩子呢  从不耍性子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是吗  很了不起呢  俊彦  在这里忍着等妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈要是能多为俊彦着想一点就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:19:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算工作再怎么忙  这样也不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都说她妈妈坏  妈妈不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  妈妈很努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  妈妈真的很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太伟大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很努力又很厉害的妈妈  太伟大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是很伟大的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装…装进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个叫俊彦的孩子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俊彦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来再来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俊彦很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  再加油荡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很高兴吧 妈妈被夸奖  被温柔地对待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔地对待他了吗  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果别有居心的话  就算温柔待人  别人也不会被治愈的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要照你的想法去做就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油收集人们受伤的心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  照你这种说法不就像在伤害别人一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 被治愈的心？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也像是好不容易治好了又被拿走了一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这个要叫什么才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个像金平糖一样所以就叫「金平糖」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金平糖…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那就把这个叫做「金平糖」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.55,0:22:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你胆大包天把我一个人丢下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过作为第一次来说做得还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.90,0:22:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次的分数就给特别送你一个100分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就保持这个状态加油吧  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  小鸠会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你不会因为得了100分就得意忘形了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.81,0:22:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚才说「就保持这个状态」…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来要保持什么状态呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.88,0:22:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  100分还是不给了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:22:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样！？
